OL,7,FMartin was told just five weeks after
OL,8,Fthe attack that he would never walk
OL,9,Fagain and has used his own experience
OL,10,Fof navigating life in a wheelchair to
OL,11,Ftry to make the world a better place
OL,12,Ffor disabled people.
OL,14,FHis book, called Top of the World,
OL,15,Fcharts life after the bombing and his
OL,16,FMount Kilimanjaro climb, for which
OL,17,Fhe's raised almost #1,000,000 for the
OL,18,FSpinal Injuries Association.
OL,20,FMartin said: "I wanted to put my own
OL,21,Fstory in my own words."
