OL,7,FSpeaking about the night of the
OL,8,Fattack, Martin said he stayed awake
OL,9,Funtil paramedics arrived and at that
OL,10,Fpoint he said he did not think he
OL,11,Fwould make it.
OL,13,FHe told a security guard to tell his
OL,14,Fwife Gabby "he loved her".
OL,16,FHe suffered PTSD from the impact of
OL,17,Fthe attack on his daughter and admits
OL,18,Fto feeling 'guilt' he couldn't protect
OL,19,Fher and has had serious bouts of
OL,20,Fsevere depression.
