OL,7,FHe described the moment he woke from a
OL,8,Fcoma in hospital a week after the
OL,9,Fbombing, when he was told he was
OL,10,Fparalysed from the waist down.
OL,12,FMartin said: "The guilt does creep in
OL,13,Fevery now and again, when I think, I
OL,14,Fshouldn't have bought those tickets.
OL,16,F"But I suppose it's my mind making
OL,17,Fsense of that night."
OL,19,FWhen Martin climbed Kilimanjaro, he
OL,20,Ftook his mum's ashes to scatter at the
OL,21,Ftop of the mountain.
